{"tid":1451871,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"呢條垃圾大陸保險婆 我都忍得你耐","createTime":"2019-08-11T21:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:11:20.000Z","uid":298721,"like":307,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c364dac631c6fa8dbfd0f03802906e2240f0cd45","tid":1451871,"uid":298721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:27:07.000Z","msg":"本身同你都冇乜兩句。作為識你嘅同事我感到無比恥辱 屌你老母大陸系 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪又係要靠香港先幫你開到單。 你條柒頭成撚日上大陸傾保單犯法架啵 你唔知架咩？ 又話自己知法守法？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQj50Ve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQj50Ve.jpg&h=ff18f8ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLAdqmV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLAdqmV.jpg&h=16d211fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xUbzUfg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUbzUfg.jpg&h=eaa379a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XrxCR1W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXrxCR1W.jpg&h=2de05863&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgW0POC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgW0POC.jpg&h=e61e8ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oq9NuO1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foq9NuO1.jpg&h=bd07c593&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uzBgn82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuzBgn82.jpg&h=8341db8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公屋咪就係比你班支那住撚哂囉 仲同我講享受香港經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。仲話14年之後唔派糖同雨傘有關。你老味啲錢去撚哂明日大愚啦<br />\n4千蚊仲有好多人未撚收到架 屌你老母支那婆 共享大灣區啦果到大撚把客啊。屌你老母。<br />\n<br />\n第一次出post sor for1999. 我太撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6767ee918b805656bf9f5c5808f2b4d978ac6218","tid":1451871,"uid":298721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"ee9468f5ed5bca214246ab813614cf2b66e80e87","tid":1451871,"uid":298721,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:28:48.000Z","msg":"香港警察知法犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n